Category: 56: Administrative and Support and Waste Management and Remediation Services
Description: This sector is analogous to WARM 42 sector for IH models. This sector is disaggregated twice: initially from from BEA '562000:Waste management and remediation services', and then from NAICS '562212' Solid waste landfilling.  This U.S. industry comprises establishments primarily engaged in (1) operating landfills for the disposal of nonhazardous solid waste or (2) the combined activity of collecting and/or hauling nonhazardous waste materials within a local area and operating landfills for the disposal of nonhazardous solid waste, related to concrete disposal. These establishments may produce byproducts such as methane.
